race.comment: NIGHT LIGHTER (2) is better than last start when fourth (17.05) from Box 6 at Mandurah over 300m. Goes very well from this draw with five wins and three minor placings from nine starts. Has ability and can bounce back. SUNSET BUBBLES (8) comes off a slick 17.33 placing at this track over 297m. Fast run latest and rates a key player again. ELITE GENERAL (6) boasts a strong record this journey here with five wins and three minors from 11 tries. Recorded a 2.5 lengths win (17.14) in a Free For All last time at this track. Can feature with the right run. KINGSBRAE EXTRA (1) has strong credentials from this draw.
